    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Sustainable, stylish, modern and useful cleaning supplies make this four piece set from Beille household and kitchen essentials! Each item in this set features durable handles made from sustainable bamboo, offering both strength and style while minimizing environmental impact. The dish brush and scrub brush are equipped with durable, high density bristles, easily tackling stubborn grime and grease on pots, pans, dishes and other household items, as well as floors, grout, tubs and tile too! The dish brushes can also be used to scrub vegetables or fruits, to clean cutting boards, your kitchen sink and more. Both dish brushes features an ergonomic bamboo palm handle, offering a comfortable and easy to hold grip when cleaning.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Beille Modern Bamboo and Confetti Household Cleaning Tools (Many Styles)</h2>\n  <p>Sustainable, stylish, modern and useful cleaning supplies make this four piece set from Beille household and kitchen essentials! Each item in this set features durable handles made from sustainable bamboo, offering both strength and style while minimizing environmental impact.</p>\n  <p>The dish brush and scrub brush are equipped with durable, high density bristles, easily tackling stubborn grime and grease on pots, pans, dishes and other household items, as well as floors, grout, tubs and tile too! The dish brushes can also be used to scrub vegetables or fruits, to clean cutting boards, your kitchen sink and more. Both dish brushes features an ergonomic bamboo palm handle, offering a comfortable and easy to hold grip when cleaning.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>HOUSEHOLD ESSENTIALS SET:</strong> Useful, modern and stylish cleaning supplies, household and kitchen essentials for every home; set includes one shower squeegee, one dish brush, one scrub brush and dust pan and brush set</li>\n    <li><strong>DISH BRUSHES:</strong> Heavy duty bristles are tough on stubborn grease and grime, ensuring a thorough clean for all your dishes, pots, pans and more; sustainable bamboo handle and high density bristles combine scrubbing efficiency and sustainability all in one</li>\n    <li><strong>BAMBOO HANDLES:</strong> Kitchen dish brush, scrubber brush, shower squeegee and dust pan and brush set all feature ergonomic and sustainable bamboo handles, offering a comfortable and easy to hold grip when cleaning</li>\n    <li><strong>MODERN DESIGN:</strong> Natural bamboo handles and pop of confetti-like color lend a stylish but organic and neutral design that will look great in any bathroom, kitchen, laundry room, garage and more</li>\n    <li><strong>CARE INSTRUCTIONS:</strong> Simply rinse off items under warm water and soap of choice and pat dry; to maximize longevity, avoid submerging bamboo in water for extended periods</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/71269/ZFUDUUlNUYPP1irm8CnPuGrEVF5WJG-metadW5kZWZpbmVkQmVpbGxlX0JhbWJvb19Db21wbGV0ZV9TZXRfNHBjX21haW5fanBnLmpwZw==-.jpg\" alt=\"Sustainable, stylish, modern and useful cleaning supplies make this four piece set from Beille household and kitchen essentials\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Multicolor</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>In addition to the dish brushes, this set includes a convenient shower squeegee too. Featuring a nine inch smooth and flexible TPR rubber blade and bamboo handle, it effectively removes water, ensuring a streak free finish on glass, mirrors and other smooth surfaces throughout the house.</p>\n  <p>Lastly, this cleaning supplies set also comes with a 13 inch dust pan and brush set. Beille’s dust pan and brush set will make quick work of dry messes in the kitchen, laundry room, garage, entryway, bathrooms and more. The dust pan itself is lightweight and easy to carry between spaces; it comes with a built in TPR rubber edge to improve debris collection efficiency, as well as built in teeth for removing unwanted materials from the brush.</p>\n  <p>All items except the small dish brush have built in hanging holes for convenient and tidy storage when not in use. Natural bamboo handle and confetti-like pop of color lend a modern and stylish meets organic and neutral design finish, that’s sure to look great in any space! Elevate your cleaning routine with these modern and stylish cleaning tools that combine style, practicality and sustainability all in one.</p>\n  <p>CARE INSTRUCTIONS: Simply rinse off dish brush under warm water and soap of choice to keep it looking fresh; to maximize longevity, avoid submerging bamboo in water for extended periods</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "Sustainable, stylish, modern and useful cleaning supplies make this four piece set from Beille household and kitchen essentials! Each item in this set features durable handles made from sustainable bamboo, offering both strength and style while minimizing environmental impact. The dish brush and scrub brush are equipped with durable, high density bristles, easily tackling stubborn grime and grease on pots, pans, dishes and other household items, as well as floors, grout, tubs and tile too! The dish brushes can also be used to scrub vegetables or fruits, to clean cutting boards, your kitchen sink and more. Both dish brushes features an ergonomic bamboo palm handle, offering a comfortable and easy to hold grip when cleaning.",
